# Negative Test Case 6: Creating Invitation With Invalid Event Time
1.  Open website invu.ge
2.  Click Login Button
3.  Enter email “dressup118@gmail.com”
4.  Enter Password “1111111111111111111”
5.  Click Sign In 
6.  Choose Template
7.  Click template card with h3 text "Minimal Birthday"
8.  Enter in Event time “90:00” (input with type='time')
9.  Click Create Invitation
Expected Result: Invitation should not be created. Error or validation message for invalid event time should be displayed.

