# Positive Test Case 6: Creating Invitation with RSVP Option
1.  Open website invu.ge
2.  Click Login Button
3.  Enter email “dressup118@gmail.com”
4.  Enter Password “1111111111111111111”
5.  Click Sign In 
6.  Choose Template
7.  Click template card with h3 text "Minimal Birthday"
8.  Enter Event Title “MG Birthday” (input with placeholder='მაგალითად, ემა და ნოას ქორწილი')
9.  Enter Event Date “17.10.2025” (input with type='date')
10. Check Allow guests to RSVP Button (input with type='checkbox' or button labeled 'RSVP')
11. Click Create Invitation

